title: Civic mindedness competes with slime at Kids' Choice Awards
text:
Civic mindedness competes with slime at Kids' Choice Awards Monday, March 26, 2018 - 01:15 
While celebrities did get covered in slime, the hot topic of the night was the March for Our Lives protests which took place around the globe. Saskia O'Donoghue reports
